# About
ThingiPano contains metadata, images, and panoramic depth-map renderings of 3D designs from Thingiverse up through 2008. 
Examples applications of the dataset are highlighted in the paper _"ThingiPano: A Large-Scale Dataset of 3D Printing Metadata, Images, and Panoramic Renderings for Exploring Design Reuse"_ to be published in IEEE MultiMedia Big Data (IEEE BigMM) 2020. 



